cu.explanation_en: Setting the GNB IPv4 address for NG AMF to an unreachable IP '10.0.0.1' will cause routing failure and prevent proper connection to the AMF.

du.explanation_en: Setting PRACH message 1 frequency start to -1 (out of range) will cause frequency misalignment and lead to PRACH configuration failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將 PRACH 訊息 1 頻率起始設定為 -1（超出範圍）會導致頻率錯位，並造成 PRACH 配置失敗。
